column5: Hello  Going fishing tomorrow at Keiffers for some small fish action.  If your out there and you see a black shelter with a big guy ina orange suit and a women in a orange jacket, pop by and say HI..  My name is Dave  Good luck tomorrow and be safe  DAve
Hope y'all have great day tomorrow, and catch some fish. Let us know how you did.
I'll look for ya, DMASSE.  I'm either gonna fish there tomorrow or Roches, epending on where I can find parking?  Goodluck.
